metadata.name: IN CASE OF EMERGENCY PLEASE SAVE MY BAGS
metadata.description:
On the night of 2/20/2022 the NFT community was in commotion due to a phishing attack on the widely used marketplace OpenSea. 
This unfortunate situation is the inspiration for this piece called "IN CASE OF EMERGENCY PLEASE SAVE MY BAGS". The NFT is on the Ethereum blockchain, stored as ERC-721 tokens, and hosted on IPFS.

This non-fungible token is minted on the 2/22/22 which also falls on a Tuesday and is marked as Twosday.

Whatever happens in the NFT space and on the Blockchain, I CASE OF EMERGENCY PLEASE SAVE MY BAGS!
